OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be rather cloudy and
OL,6,Fbreezy across many northern and
OL,7,Fnorthwestern areas, with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain at times. Elsewhere, after a grey
OL,9,Fand in places misty start with patchy
OL,10,Frain in the west, some very warm
OL,11,Fsunshine developing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBreezy, with rain spreading
OL,14,Fnortheastwards across Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fand Scotland this evening, then some
OL,16,Fclearer spells overnight. Mostly clear
OL,17,FEngland and Wales, though patchy fog
OL,18,Fand drizzle in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
