OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FPatchy rain and fog in the
OL,6,Fnorthwest, and some western areas at
OL,7,Ffirst. Otherwise dry with a good deal
OL,8,Fof very warm or hot sunshine
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Breezy in the northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
